</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-41_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulation</strong> - The process of monitoring and enforcing laws and standards to ensure legal compliance and protect public interests.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-43_ pf-text-1"><strong>Ethics </strong>- Principles and standards that guide the conduct of professionals, ensuring integrity, accountability, and fairness.

