</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-53_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong>Adherence to the Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA) standards</strong></h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-55_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA) sets the regulatory framework for solicitors in England and Wales. The Law Society collaborates closely with the SRA to ensure members adhere to these standards. Key regulations include:




























