</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-62_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong>Implementation of ethical practices</strong></h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-64_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Law Society emphasises the importance of ethics in legal practice. Solicitors must adhere to the highest ethical standards, which include maintaining client confidentiality, avoiding conflicts of interest, and ensuring transparency in billing practices.






























