</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-77_ pf-text-1"><strong>Stay informed on regulatory changes</strong> - Keeping abreast of changes in legislation and regulations is crucial. Solicitors should regularly consult the Law Society's resources and updates to ensure compliance with the latest legal standards.







